jodd.mail

Class EmailAddress

  • java.lang.Object
    • jodd.mail.EmailAddress

  • public class EmailAddress
extends java.lang.Object
    Storage for personal name and email address. Serves as an email address adapter between various formats.

      • of

        public static EmailAddress of(java.lang.String address)
        Creates new address by specifying one of the following:
        • "foo@bar.com" - only email address.
        • "Jenny Doe &lt;foo@bar.com&gt;" - first part of the string is personal name, and the other part is email, surrounded with < and >.
        Parameters:
        address - String containing address to convert.
